* When the dance was done

01:17:29.278 --> 01:17:32.882
* When I went my way

01:17:32.916 --> 01:17:39.956
* When I tried to find
rainbows far away

01:17:39.989 --> 01:17:43.392
* All the lovely lights

01:17:43.426 --> 01:17:47.096
* Seemed to fade from view

01:17:47.130 --> 01:17:50.734
* They were you
They were you

01:17:50.767 --> 01:17:54.403
* They were you

01:17:54.437 --> 01:18:01.210
BOTH:
* Without you near me

01:18:01.911 --> 01:18:07.416
* I can't see

01:18:08.351 --> 01:18:15.191
* When you're near me

01:18:15.224 --> 01:18:20.296
* Wonderful things come to be

01:18:22.098 --> 01:18:25.935
* Every secret prayer

01:18:25.969 --> 01:18:29.472
* Every fancy free

01:18:29.505 --> 01:18:36.780
* Everything I dared
for both you and me

01:18:36.813 --> 01:18:40.283
* All my wildest dreams

01:18:40.316 --> 01:18:44.287
* Multiplied by two

01:18:44.320 --> 01:18:46.189
* They were you

01:18:46.222 --> 01:18:48.057
* They were you

01:18:48.091 --> 01:18:51.260
* They were you

01:18:53.362 --> 01:18:57.200
* They were you

01:18:57.233 --> 01:18:59.368
* They were you

01:19:01.470 --> 01:19:06.776
* They were you

01:19:28.531 --> 01:19:30.299
I missed you, Matt.

01:19:31.000 --> 01:19:33.336
I missed you, too.

01:19:33.369 --> 01:19:35.104
Here, maybe I can
stop your bleeding.

01:19:35.138 --> 01:19:36.505
You already have.

01:19:43.379 --> 01:19:45.248
You've been hurt too.

01:19:48.551 --> 01:19:51.154
Look, it's beginning to snow.

01:19:52.221 --> 01:19:53.990
I know.
Here.

01:19:54.991 --> 01:19:56.359
Take my coat.

01:19:57.426 --> 01:19:59.395
Both.

01:19:59.428 --> 01:20:01.564
There's room there
for both.

01:20:11.040 --> 01:20:15.144
* Love! You are love!

01:20:15.178 --> 01:20:16.880
* You are love!

01:20:16.913 --> 01:20:23.252
* Better far than a metaphor
can ever, ever be

01:20:24.387 --> 01:20:26.990
* Love!
* You are love!

01:20:27.023 --> 01:20:28.457
* You are love!

01:20:28.491 --> 01:20:31.060
* You are love!

01:20:32.328 --> 01:20:34.964
* My mystery

01:20:34.998 --> 01:20:38.167
* My mystery

01:20:40.269 --> 01:20:42.939
* Of Love!

01:20:42.972 --> 01:20:44.373
BELLOMY:
Look, they've come back.

01:20:44.407 --> 01:20:46.042
HUCKLEBEE:
It's a miracle.

01:20:46.075 --> 01:20:47.476
They're home.

01:20:49.245 --> 01:20:50.346
Matt!

01:20:52.481 --> 01:20:53.883
Luisa.

01:20:55.919 --> 01:21:02.091
EL GALLO:
* Try to remember
the kind of September

01:21:02.125 --> 01:21:08.597
* When life was slow
and oh, so mellow

01:21:08.631 --> 01:21:15.071
* Try to remember
the kind of September

01:21:15.104 --> 01:21:21.610
* When grass was green
and grain was yellow

01:21:21.644 --> 01:21:27.984
* Try to remember
the kind of September

01:21:28.017 --> 01:21:34.623
* When you were
a tender and callow fellow

01:21:34.657 --> 01:21:40.663
* Try to remember,
and if you remember

01:21:40.696 --> 01:21:42.298
* Then follow

01:21:47.670 --> 01:21:53.409
* Deep in December,
it's nice to remember

01:21:53.442 --> 01:21:59.648
* Although you know
the snow will follow

01:21:59.682 --> 01:22:05.388
* Deep in December,
it's nice to remember

01:22:05.421 --> 01:22:11.594
* Without a hurt
the heart is hollow

01:22:11.627 --> 01:22:17.466
* Deep in December,
it's nice to remember

01:22:17.500 --> 01:22:23.039
* The fire of September
that made us mellow

